      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">PPSh SMG teams from this Unit can Shoot while Mounted on Armoured Tank teams (to a maximum of one PPSh SMG team per Tank), and can Dismount when Charging into Contact.</characteristic>
